Jennifer Fry (amụrụ na 24 Machị 1989) bụ onye egwuregwu badminton nke South Africa. Ọ bụ onye nrite ọla edo nke 2015 All-Africa Games na ngwakọta abụọ, nwetakwara nrite ọla ọcha na ngwakọta otu. N'afọ 2017, o nwetara ihe nrite ọla edo abụọ na 2017 African Championship, merie aha ahụ n'ihe omume ụmụ nwanyị na ngwakọta abụọ.
